l continents still. This is however a sad story. At Lvl 18, I died in Kithicor Forest by a run away gang of undead. I never got that stuff back. Un-twinked at LvL 18 and worth 3K. ( Swear to god, I'm got so lucky on that char.) I tried to teach Language again for the money to replace that stuff. But EQ put in some bug that made it take a ton longer to teach at that time. **** YOU EQ FOR SCREWING MY PERFECT PLAN!!!<br> <br></p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
